<b>Subject:</b> Tailoring Question<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR></STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>I am now (and have been for a bit) at a tailoring skill level in which I can no longer advance without making more advanced items (i.e. Studded leather items). Are there certain items that are easier to make at first, such as gorget or boots vs. tunic's and pants? Which items should I begin my attempts of constuction?

<P>I've made only about 3 attempts and have failed each time so far with a tailoring skill of 30+, and obviously it is quite a bit more expensive to experiment at this point (1 plat ea for the studs if bought, and I certainly can't make them!).
<P>Any information along these lines would be appreciated.
<P>Nesif
<BR>Cleric of Innoruuk
